name: Chentu Chek
content:
Chentu Chek was a male Human member of the Bounty Hunters' Guild. A 23-year veteran of the Guild, Chek served as Armory Master, sometime during the tenure of Cradossk as the Guild's Head.
During his time as Armory Master, Chentu had contributed to the Bounty Hunters Guild Handbook. Titled "Tools of the Trade", Chek's contribution to the handbook covered weapons, tech, vehicles, and traps.
